sing, malformed, or inconsistent data safely | [BOOLEAN HANDLING RULE] Normalize boolean values before comparison | [DATA CONSISTENCY RULE] Respect dataset schema | [SUPPORT FILES RULE] If env/config is used, include: 1. Instructional sentence 2. File content in markdown code block 3. BEFORE the main code | [DIFFICULTY RULE] Complexity MUST match level | [FORMAT RULE] Only valid markdown code blocks allowed | [LANGUAGE TAG RULE] ALWAYS label markdown code blocks with the correct underlying programming language (e.g., python, javascript, sql) | [OUTPUT FORMAT RULE] Monetary values formatted with '$', commas, 2 decimals | [DIFFICULTY CONSISTENCY RULE] All challenges MUST have similar complexity and length, even if coding styles differ | [HEADER RULE - STRICT] You MUST start your entire response EXACTLY with this markdown block (do not print anything before it):
